<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the documentation, it claims the current ZF version supports Lucene index format 2.1 while the coming ZF 1.6 will support 2.3.</p>

<p>These indices are backwards compatible (newer code should be able to read older indices in the Java world). However, it is very difficult to glean from the inaccurate / confusing documentation which version of ZF matches with which version of Lucene index.</p>

